In java the Strings are Onjects.

String Length

A string length is an object, Which contins methods that can perform certain operations on strings.

For example the length of a string  can be found with .length() method.

EX: string="djbegksnggnjshjhxdfghjdfcgvhbncfgvbhn";
 
   System.out.println("The length of the string is:" + .length());

Somemore methods in java are:
 .toUpperCase()
 .toLowerCase()


 
